{"tid":120962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大粒嘢亂入！當奴侵拉著安倍晉三突襲婚禮現場","createTime":"2017-02-15T00:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T00:18:22.000Z","uid":44025,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8765b0120d8c0c29358e3750152ced9b0ac1fcfc","tid":120962,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:15:54.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統當奴侵11日和日本首相安倍晉三在佛羅里達州棕櫚灘的馬阿拉歌（Mar-a-Lago）俱樂部共進晚餐，當奴侵竟然心血來潮的拉著安倍晉三突襲婚禮現場，對新人送上祝福，嚇壞了出席婚禮的賓客。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，當奴侵、安倍晉三亂入婚禮的影片和照片，日前被與會的賓客發布在社群媒體上；見證「大粒嘢亂入」的理查（Rich7 DeAgazio）在臉書上留言表示，「天殺的！我剛看完他們回應北韓試射飛彈的新聞，然後真人就出現在這裡，當奴侵、安倍晉三，全場的焦點」。<br />\n<br />\n當奴侵、安倍晉三亂入的婚禮，新郎是33歲的卡爾亨利（Carl Henry Lindner IV），新娘是凡內莎（Vanessa Jane Falk），而新郎的父親是美國金融集團AFG行政總裁，新郎的父親還曾捐款贊助當奴侵競選總統。<br />\n<br />\n「大粒嘢亂入」的影片中，當奴侵在對新人送上祝福時，大方的表示「我剛剛和日本首相安倍晉三說，走啦，我們來這裡看看」，引起現場賓客一陣歡聲笑語，當奴侵還代替安倍晉三，祝福這對新人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpHbwzWD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpHbwzWD.jpg&h=11658895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1L7W01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1L7W01.jpg&h=6d5d1409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1975337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1975337&d=NZQUy3Ple5IgpjsjUCCfIjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=8346c03e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1975337&h=72f19537\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1975337</a>"},{"pid":"2c07c60de6a00149f1a5bd9b7aee5127c4dceee1","tid":120962,"uid":37933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:23:52.000Z","msg":"maroon 5咩屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.